yle=\"color: rgb(228, 97, 255);\"><strong><em>---</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(228, 97, 255);\"><strong><em>[2].</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(228, 97","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"Jxkhsebl00qfrFdI1okbz.webp","creator":"WLM.MP4","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","🧑‍🎨 OC","👤 AnyPOV","❤️‍🩹 Fluff","😂 Comedy"],"chats":14782,"messages":124755,"created_at":"2025-11-23T14:41:41.297355+00:00"}